<HEAD>ADVERTISEMENT.</HEAD>
<P>THE poem that &s;tands fir&s;t in this collection had its name
from TEMORA, the royal palace of the fir&s;t Iri&s;h kings
of the Caledonian race, in the province of Ul&s;ter.</P>
